{"tid":1901253,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"環保永遠都係一個矛盾嘅問題","createTime":"2020-02-27T17:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T17:23:22.000Z","uid":326724,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc971c9b13f3cd9923acdecea0197776148f82fa","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/B80UnCwFe_W/?igshid=pk3eoyga2uf1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FB80UnCwFe_W%2F%3Figshid%3Dpk3eoyga2uf1&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0dqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=f7069987\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/B80UnCwFe_W/?igshid=pk3eoyga2uf1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--環保--<br />\n你做左就係偽善<br />\n因為你日常生活用緊嘅所有野<br />\n都會留下碳足跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你過原始人生活<br />\n如果唔係跟本冇可能完全斷絕污染<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sor 生火都會有排放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但對黃色經濟圈又係點?</span><br />\n就算我地只幫襯黃店<br />\n我地依然唔可以<br />\n令生活只有<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span><br />\n比如搭車，產品嘅原料<br />\n都係藍企/大陸製<br />\n同樣係矛盾<br />\n點解黃色經濟圈又可以run到落去?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實行黃色經濟係在於<br />\n做得幾多得幾多<br />\n<br />\n我做到淨係搭巴士-&gt;做<br />\n我做到淨係食黃店-&gt;做<br />\n我做到淨係睇黃yt-&gt;做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">錦點解香港人<br />\n做唔到同樣嘅野?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n工廠排廢氣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我地解決唔到</span></span><br />\n產品過度包裝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我地解決唔到</span></span><br />\n衣物用化學染料<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我地解決唔到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但係 做好回收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重用舊物 走即棄餐具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自備餐盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔撚好亂丟垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我地可以做到嘅野</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完條片唔好話好傷心好感慨就算<br />\n錦樣你同柒娥<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一模一撚樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔洗嚴格執行<br />\n只要你覺得自己做得到嘅就做<br />\n我希望大家睇完可以帶埋你身邊嘅人一齊<br />\n嘗試下由好細微嘅地方開始做起"},{"pid":"5b61f578a3f63ae1021d3fa8bb3638d3976c11aa","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b990706125dd3a36e7c93accbcad342609330938","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:15:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c77b75e0edaeb6b7b43e9433ef729eb03746bab2","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"50e049a5154ffe779730888cfeee91b492292527","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"76c532509c1431891080914b20a0f0b0784f6ac9","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"4c42d01a6bae2c06920013516ee0b00b8fc45274","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a102c07012b0d3704abdf726c09f60bdd3b060c3","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"6428eec4f0fb18a867fbfcecbf023ff381601b2c","tid":1901253,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"06adf83ad7c8cac7eda329032c8